author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Discord and their recent actions in banning "Ro-cleaner", this was a bot designed to keep minors separate from users interacting on more mature servers. It had it's problems but overall was a good stopgap solution to stop the rampant disgusting behaviour on the platform, behavior that should be tackled by Discord and Roblox first. Thanks for watching!

title: Discord Banned a Child Safety Bot...
